Burnt karambwan is the result of accidentally burning a raw karambwan while attempting to make a cooked karambwan. The burn rate while cooking these will decrease as players reach higher Cooking levels, stopping entirely at level 99.

The burnt karambwan has no use whatsoever. Like most other burnt food, it is tradeable to other players but not on the Grand Exchange.
